videos.headline: Drake's Anna Miller hits a buzzer-beater to win Missouri Valley championship
videos.description: Courtney Becker finds Anna Miller in the paint, and she rises up to sink a buzzer-beating game winner for Drake in 76-75 battle vs. Missouri State.
